_ww-text_text.en: At Systemak, we are committed to protecting your privacy. When you use our system or sign in with Google, we may collect the following data: Your email address. Your display name from Google. Your profile picture (if available). How we use your data: We only use your data to activate your account and provide a personalized experience. We will never sell or share your data with third parties without your consent. We may use your email to send updates or promotional offers related to the system. Data Protection: Your data is stored securely following industry standards. You have the right to request data deletion at any time by contacting us. Contact Us: For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: 📧 support@systmak.com
